OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering daytime showers will ease
OL,7,Fthis evening leaving a dry night with
OL,8,Fclear spells for a while. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly with a patchy frost before
OL,10,Ffurther cloud arrives from the
OL,11,Fsouthwest by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,14,Fbut cloud and some patchy rain will
OL,15,Fgradually spread across the region.
OL,16,FRemaining cloudy into the afternoon
OL,17,Fwith some heavier rain arriving
OL,18,Fovernight. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
