OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FFurther rain and strong winds on
OL,7,FWednesday, with sunshine and showers
OL,8,Fon Thursday. Showers more isolated on
OL,9,FFriday. Feeling a little warmer than
OL,10,Fof late, especially in any sunshine.
